{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was in a building called [GERMAN], which means a circle of friends, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't translate it exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was actually a men's club, a Jewish men's club.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The men would come and play cards and spend the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the building was owned by a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They needed a caterer, and since my mother had come from the hotel industry and was very familiar with that sort of thing, we drifted into it without any problem.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my dad was the manager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother did the cooking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We actually did not cook dinners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was just lunch and afternoon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In Germany, everybody is into snacks, and into coffee, and desserts, and that kind of thing, and-- but big lunches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The three of us, we were the waitresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I should have been in school then-- by then, because I was getting to be 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But my parents needed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I did not go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Neither did my sister Margot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This went on for a while, until the Nazis decided that the Jews did not need to socialize-- whether it was men or women, didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they just closed the building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, who had a lot of audacity, decided at that time that if this was successful, why not open a Jewish restaurant?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We discussed the merits, and we thought it was a good idea, but we didn't like what he had in mind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First place, he picked a location, which was very audacious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not an off street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was right in the downtown section right near the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was an empty apartment, I think, above some stores.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
